values: So i went to the job corps dentist last wendsday because my gums were sore and i didn't know why. Aperantly They are infected. When a new tooth grows in it loosens the gums and makes it possible for food to get stuck down in there. So that is why i am going to the dentist today. Damn you wisdome tooth. The lone tooth. I bet they'll take it out. Its almost fully grown. So after the dentist mary wants to go christmas shopping. That will be fun, I hope. I need to remember my wallet.

I am about to leave for job corps once again. If i can ever get my dad unglued from the tv. The weekend was... depressing. I had a little fun at my b-day party. But i didn't get to spend much time with Eric. At least not any alone time. There is always someone here to bother us. I wasted my money on a round trip ticket. Thats like $20 wasted. I guess this weekend just wasn't much fun for me. Other than the birthday party. Eric and Teif got me Karoke Revolution so we played that alot. Its a great game. So much fun! Well thats all i care to say right now. Elinor is as selfish as always and i'll leave it at that.
Sometimes i just feel like he could be making more of an effort. I feel unimportant to him. Am i not important to you?

All i have to say this thanksgiving is, What the fuck is going on? I think mary has cancled it. She is yelling at my dad as we speek. This is just horrible. She could have just left instead of canceling. Now what am i going to do? I just wish i knew why she is so mad. I feel so alone.

So i am going back to Job corps in a few minutes. Its not for long though because i go on ad-leave friday. I'll be here at my mums helping out as best i can. Elinor is coming over for halloween. I need to call her and ask if she can pick me up. It would make things easier on mom. I miss Eric. I wish i could see him. Its going to be awhile until i can get home again. I wonder when that will be. I think probably vetrens day weekend. We get an extra day off. Well i have to go and i am drawing a blank on what to type.

I am really agry at Eric. Its makes me sad. I never thought i could get this agry at him. Its almost hate. I was talking on the phone with him and he wasn't really listening to me. It had been a really bad day and all i wanted was for him to listen. His comp was broken and he was fixing it. I even tryed telling him that i was going to go so he could focus on his comp (trying to get him to stop because i was annoyed) but he said no so i stayed on. He kept tinkering with his comp and it pissed me off so much i hung up on him. I then went strait to bed. I know he called me back and said he was sorry but i was too angry to get up and take the call. I haven't called him since its been a day now. I was hoping he would call me. I would have run to the phone just knowing that he cared. Say i'm sorry and express how i feel. But he never called. I think i might call him tonight. I called my friend Daniel. The one who got sent home. He seems to be doing alot better. Hes relaxing playing FF9. It was good to hear him in such a good mood. Back to his old joking self. well thats All for now.

I thought this was funny
Your Daddy Is Darth Vader

Who's Your Daddy?

My bus leaves 11:30pm monday. I have no way to get into seattle except the metro. And i really don't like the idea of walking around seattle alone at night with all my belongings strapped to my back. Eric is still here he is watching "One Peice" with Elinor. Its his b-day and i wish i could do more for him. We have been lazily watching tv all day. I talked to Elinor so she is now clear on all that happend. i want to go i suddenly feel really sad.

I am home until monday! The combination of a special pass and a three day weekend! Today would have been great if the bus i was going to take accually ran on thursdays. And elinor didn't break the car in seattle and have to call for help get a tow truck and pick me up 3 hours after i got in seattle. So i got into seattle at 6pm and didn't get home until 10pm and by then Eric couldn't come over. So i am bummed. Glad to be home but wishing Eric was here. Its a long story if i go into details and i am too tired to write more. I am going to bed.

Overall I had a blast this weekend. I never did get to try ddr. I wanted to. Oh well. I got to try a bunch of other games. City of heros, Jak X, and some others. I played D&D for the first time i thought it was cool. I hope to play again someday. Well i cant think of much to write. I had alot of fun. I hope to do it again next year.

I want to go to Pax again today but my dad wont wake up. Its pissing me off. Mc Chris was awsome! So was Mc Frontalot. They were awsome. The mini bosses were good too but i only got to stick around for one song. It was a blast. We ran into Tycho so many times. Eric really likes him so that was kind of cool Tycho even said Eric was his number one fan. It was cool. Well my dad finnally woke up so hopfully we will be leaving soon. Theres nothing to eat. I really should eat somthing before i go. There were leftover pankakes but apperantly elinor ate them all. This is the only chance i will get to write before i have to go back to job corps. Yesterday was alot of fun. I dressed up in my visas costume and was complemented by tycho and Mc Chris. So that was cool. I bout all three of Mc Chris's cds and got them all signed. Man its 10:00 doors are open and i am still stuck here at home. I am so agrivated right now. Dad decided to take a shower. Well atleast i wont have to wait in line. I wish i didn't have to go back to job corps so soon. I have to work 5-1 in the kitchen next week. That means i have to wake up at 4:30 to be ready in time for my shift. It sucks but i hear it is the better of the two. the other shift is 10-6. I wish i could have spent more time with Eric. Its really hard being away from him. I might just have

So its almost noon and Eric was still in bed. Good thing i called him before i got here or he would have still been asleep. So he is in the shower and i am bored. My dad calls me shortly after he left to call a slugbug silver. That made me laugh a bit. I winder what the plan is for today.  well again a short entry.

Well I am leaving in 20 min. I am really dreading it but not as much as i did when i woke up. I had breakfast even though i didn't feel hungry. Eggs and bacon, yum... Eric is just now waking up. I hope he isn't too sad. He says he is just tired. I am so bad with goodbyes. They always seem like forever at the time but its only a week, or a month until i come visit again. I may go threw withdrawls but i'll live. At least i have culinary waiting for me. I watch the time tick by and pray it slows down so every second is like a minute and i can stay that much longer. I may be sad now but i know its not the end of the world and life goes on and all that. My future is more important than anything i might be feeling right now. and thats all i have to say i guess. I'll update as soon as i can. Wish me luck and a speedy return.

Well i have to say as the time goes by i seem to be growing more sad. i guess its because i am leaving tomorrow. I Feel like crying but i don't want to upset eric. Its my last night with him and i want to make the best of it. But this sadness keeps me from being happy. I saw the willy wonka movie. i have to say it was utterly terrifieing. And even though i cant spell you know what i mean. i think that is all i want to say right now.
